structure.unit: STOCK INSURANCE COMPANIES -- OTHER THAN LIFE (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 105, sec. 21, effective June 17, 1948. -- Repealed 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 14, effective October 1, 1947. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 762b-29, 762b-30.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Unfair discrimination or nonuniform deviation in fire insurance rates prohibited.
